CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 20, 1951, pg. 2, reads: "Leaders Attend Dinner - Dr. Grace Loucks Elliott, executive director of the National YWCA, New York, addressed a group of church and community leaders in East Liberty 'Y.' The dinner meeting climaxed a two-day institute.  Left photo: the Rev. J. A. Williams, paster of Baptist Temple Church, Mrs. Elliott and Mrs. Grace McCray, chairman of the Religious Resource Committee of the Centre Avenue branch.... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait from left: Rev. J. A. Williams, Dr. Grace Loucks Elliott, and Grace McCray, standing in East Liberty YWCA
